   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession">
            <pb n="1"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__549" type="place">N.</rs>
                  <date when="1912-04-13">13.4.1912</date> Potsdamerstr 50-51.
                    </dateline>
               <salute>Dear <rs type="person" ref="#tillich_person_id__1928">friend</rs>,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Last evening I have written a long letter, but perhaps it will be better not to
                    send it off. <rs ref="#tillich_person_id__2128" type="person">Fräulein
                        Zschorsch</rs> came to me this afternoon, in order to write to you also
                    some lines. But at last she was not in the mood. <pb n="2"/> I dont know, if you
                    got the letter I sent to you the day before you left <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__549" type="place">Nauen</rs>? – <rs ref="#tillich_person_id__2128" type="person">Fräulein Zschorsch</rs> and I
                    wish to know what time of the day suits you best to meet us in <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__37" type="place">Berlin</rs>; we are intending to
                    come up to <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__37" type="place">B.</rs> very <pb n="3"/> soon. And could you arrange to pass some
                    hours with us? Let me have the two last sermons, as you have promised me!
                    Please? – What are you doing all day long?</p>
            <closer>
               <signed>
                  <hi rend="u">
                     <rs type="person" ref="#tillich_person_id__2012">Elisabeth</rs>
                  </hi>
               </signed>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
